text: One if my favorite memories is coming home from school one Fall and having no homework the next day, so I got to sit down and play this game the rest of the day. I remember starting this level and instantly thinking how incredible the music sounded and fit with the theme of the level. It was so good that it was what urged me to start taking note of my favorite video game soundtracks and was one of the first I added to my playlist.
